                <h2 class="section-heading">Where and when?</h2>
                <p class="lead">The tournament takes place in the URD (restaurant) of the Huygens building. The address is Heyendaalseweg 135. It will take place on the 25th of February 2016 from 18:00h until 04:00h. Make sure you don't let your team mates and opponents down, be on time! You can arrive anywhere between 17:30h and 18:00h.</p>
